OL,6,FFive Bulgarians - Galina Nikolova, 38,
OL,7,FStoyan Stoyanov, 27, Tsvetka Todorova,
OL,8,F52, Gyunesh Ali, 33, and Patritsia
OL,9,FPaneva, 26 - admitted to fraud and
OL,10,Fmoney laundering related offences at
OL,11,FWood Green Crown Court for their
OL,12,Finvolvement in a multimillion-pound
OL,13,Fscam on the benefit system.
OL,15,FBetween October 2016 and May 2021, the
OL,16,Forganised crime group made thousands
OL,17,Fof false claims for Universal Credit
OL,18,Fusing either real people or hijacked
OL,19,Fidentities.
