OL,6,FThese claims were supported by an
OL,7,Farray of forged documents, including
OL,8,Ffictitious tenancy agreements,
OL,9,Fcounterfeit payslips, and forged
OL,10,Fletters from landlords, employers, and
OL,11,FGPs.
OL,13,FIf they were rejected, the fraudsters
OL,14,Fwould keep trying until they were
OL,15,Fgranted.
OL,17,FFraudster throws cash around and at
OL,18,Fwoman, leaving hundreds of #20
OL,19,Fscattered across the floor
