OL,6,FAfter four-and-a-half-years of fraud,
OL,7,Fthe five defendants were arrested on
OL,8,FMay 5, 2021.
OL,10,FTheir properties were raided and
OL,11,Fhundreds of "claim packs" containing
OL,12,Fforged and false documents were found
OL,13,Fand seized.
OL,15,FBundles of cash stuffed in shopping
OL,16,Fbags and suitcases, a luxury car and
OL,17,Fdesigner goods including watches,
OL,18,Fjackets, and glasses were also
OL,19,Fdiscovered in the raid.
