OL,6,FFollowing his release under
OL,7,Finvestigation, one of the five
OL,8,Fdefendants, Ali, fled the country to
OL,9,FBulgaria. But he was extradited back
OL,10,Fto the UK on February 25, 2023 so he
OL,11,Fcould face trial.
OL,13,FThe DWP, which ran the investigation,
OL,14,Fconfronted the defendants with
OL,15,Fevidence including encrypted messages,
OL,16,FCCTV footage, forged documents, seized
OL,17,Fdigital devices and bank statements,
OL,18,Fleading them to all plea guilty.
