OL,6,FBen Reid, Specialist Prosecutor for
OL,7,Fthe CPS, said: "For a number of years,
OL,8,Fthese defendants conspired to commit
OL,9,Findustrial-scale fraud against the
OL,10,FUniversal Credit system, costing the
OL,11,Ftaxpayer more than #50 million.
OL,13,F"Submitting thousands of false claims,
OL,14,Fthe organised criminals enriched
OL,15,Fthemselves from government funds
OL,16,Fdesigned to protect and help the most
OL,17,Fvulnerable people in our society.
