OL,6,F"This was a complex and challenging
OL,7,Fcase which required close and
OL,8,Feffective working between CPS
OL,9,Fprosecutors, the Department for Work
OL,10,Fand Pensions and our international
OL,11,Fpartners in both Bulgaria and through
OL,12,Fthe UK desk at Eurojust, to dismantle
OL,13,Fand successfully prosecute the
OL,14,Forganised crime group."
OL,16,FThe CPS and DWP will now work to
OL,17,Fconfiscate any of the money gained by
OL,18,Fthe gang through crime.
