OL,6,FMel Stride MP, Secretary of State for
OL,7,Fthe Department for Work and Pensions,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I am immensely proud of DWP
OL,9,Finvestigators' work, in collaboration
OL,10,Fwith the Crown Prosecution Service, to
OL,11,Ftake down this organised crime group.
OL,13,F"Today's convictions underline our
OL,14,Fcommitment to protecting taxpayers'
OL,15,Fmoney and it is only right and fair
OL,16,Fthat we bring to justice those
OL,17,Fstealing from the public purse.
